safety.description:
Every outing is organized evaluating:

• weather;
• wind;
• sea;
• participants' experience;
• comfort;
• logistics.

If conditions are not adequate, we change itinerary or program.

We prefer to cancel an outing rather than improvise.

quotes.description:
The sea changes every day.

That's why we organize customized programs based on:

• level;
• number of people;
• weather;
• chosen activity;
• special requests;
• desired experience.
